45:02.479 --> 45:06.447
♪ "Oh, take your time ♪

45:06.483 --> 45:10.251
♪ Don't live too fast ♪

45:10.286 --> 45:14.489
♪ Troubles will come ♪

45:14.524 --> 45:18.159
♪ And they will pass ♪

45:18.194 --> 45:21.229
♪ You'll find a woman ♪

45:21.264 --> 45:26.134
♪ Yeah, and you'll find love ♪

45:26.169 --> 45:28.002
♪ And don't forget, son" ♪

45:28.037 --> 45:32.740
[all] ♪ "There is
someone up above" ♪

45:32.776 --> 45:34.275
All right!

45:34.310 --> 45:37.645
♪ "And be a simple ♪

45:37.680 --> 45:41.315
